Definition: a highly fissionable isotope of plutonium that is used in atomic weapons and as a reactor fuel
Example: produced by irradiating uranium 238 with slow electrons
Synonyms: plutonium, a, highly, fissionable, isotope, of, that, is, used, in, atomic, weapons, and, as, reactor, fuel, produced, by, irradiating, uranium, with, slow, electrons
Category: noun.substance
